A Reversi game written in ActionScript. It's designed to run on any device that supports Flash/AIR, regardless of screen size.

Project was forked from iReverse Project done by Christian Cantrell

http://www.github.com/cantrell/Reversi/

It's designed for Blackberry Tablet OS

Roadmap:
- 1.0: Publish fully functional Version to Blackberry AppWorld
- 1.1: Add improvements to SinglePlayer AI and UI Design
- 1.2: Add Trophies and Rewards
